EN: Travel to the countryside and enjoy the nature scenery.

ZH: 山脚下的风景是那么宁静和美丽。
EN: The scenery at the foot of the mountain is so peaceful and beautiful.

ZH: 不同的季节会呈现不同的风景。
EN: Different seasons present different scenery.

ZH: 在公园里漫步，欣赏到了优美的风景。
EN: Strolling in the park, I enjoyed the beautiful scenery.

ZH: 这里的风景像一幅画一样迷人。
EN: The scenery here is as charming as a painting.

