EN: The scenery of this lake leaves a profound impression on people.

ZH: 雨后的风景更加清爽和明亮。
EN: The scenery after the rain is fresher and brighter.

ZH: 登上山顶，俯瞰整个城市的风景。
EN: Climbing to the top of the mountain, we overlooked the scenery of the whole city.

